#define szHelp L"pwt v0.2 Beta\r\nCopyright (C) 2016-2018 Yuri213212\r\nSite:https://github.com/Yuri213212/pwt\r\nEmail: yuri213212@vip.qq.com\r\nLicense: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0\r\nhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\r\n\r\nPlace tokens on the intersection point of the pentagram alternately.\r\nBut, once your tokens can compose a triangle with the edges, you lose.\r\nIf all 10 tokens are placed safely, the game ends in tie.\r\n\r\nPlayer1 is the offensive side and player2 is the defensive side.\r\nPlayer1 use blue tokens and player2 use pink tokens.\r\nClick near enough to the empty intersection point to place your token.\r\nThe latest placed token is marked with a white X at the center.\r\n\r\nYou can let AI determine the next move.\r\nJuniorAI (J key) will only try to avoid suicide.\r\nSeniorAI (S key) knows the place resulting the best ending.\r\n\r\nPress 'New Game' (Esc key) to reset the board for the next game."
